txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the invaders from the east surrounding Sûri-kylä. Deliver the items to Kaleva at the Lossoth capital.
'It is good to see that the invaders are being driven away. Thank you.'
'When the wind came from the east, so too came the agents of the wind. They invade our lands and take up land that was once Lossoth land.'
A Lossoth, Kaleva, at Sûri-kylä is collecting broken wooden clubs at the Lossoth capital.
Deliver the broken wooden clubs to Kaleva at Sûri-kylä in Forochel
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver broken wooden clubs from the Angmarim invaders surrounding Sûri-kylä in Forochel. The items are to be delivered to Kaleva at the Lossoth capital.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the invaders from the east surrounding Sûri-kylä.
